 	/**
 	 * Return the file extention of the given file pathname
 	 *  
	 * @author Stéphane Mangin <stephane.mangin@freesbee.fr>
 	 * 
 	 * FIXME: use of Optional should welcomed ! Or add a helper method to detect format with file headers
